				<main role="main" class=""><article class="main-content-home"><h1 class="">Welcome to Tombstone USD #1</h1>
<div class="pom-container"><p style="text-align: center; font-style: italic;font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 2em;" class="">#growinglegends</p></div>
<div class="pom-container"><p class=""><strong class="">District Office: (520) 457-2217<br>Huachuca City School: (520) 456-9842<br>Walter J. Meyer: (520) 457-3371<br>Tombstone High School: (520) 457-2215</strong></p></div>
<h2 class="" style="margin-top: 0px;">News and Tidbits</h2>
<div class="pom-container"><div class="pom-container"><div class="pom-container"><div class="pom-container">
